OL,3,CCooking oil contamination scandal
OL,4,Csparks outrage in China
OL,6,FThere is growing anger and disgust in
OL,7,FChina after it was revealed that
OL,8,FChinese companies have been using the
OL,9,Fsame oil tankers to transport fuel and
OL,10,Fcooking oil, without cleaning the
OL,11,Fvessels in between.
OL,13,FThe allegations were made in an expose
OL,14,Fby The Beijing News which found it was
OL,15,Fan "open secret" in the transport
OL,16,Findustry that tankers were being used
OL,17,Ffor dual purposes.
