OL,3,CCooking oil contamination scandal
OL,4,Csparks outrage in China
OL,6,FThe investigation found several
OL,7,Ftankers were routinely transporting
OL,8,Fedible oils, such as cooking oils or
OL,9,Fsyrup having also carried industrial
OL,10,Fwaste, liquid coal, chemicals, and
OL,11,Ffuels without proper decontamination
OL,12,Fprocesses in place.
OL,14,FChina's largest grain storage and
OL,15,Ftransport company Sinograin and a
OL,16,Fcorporation called Hopefull Grain and
OL,17,FOil Group are both named in the report
OL,18,Fand have launched their own
OL,19,Finvestigations into the alleged
OL,20,Fmalpractice.
