OL,6,FThe scandal has been reported in state
OL,7,Fmedia, indicating there was no attempt
OL,8,Fby the government to censor the
OL,9,Finitial report.
OL,11,FThere has been some censorship of
OL,12,Fdiscussions online, but it hasn't
OL,13,Fstopped millions of people expressing
OL,14,Ftheir outrage and fear as the country
OL,15,Ffaces another food scandal.
