OL,3,CCooking oil contamination scandal
OL,4,Csparks outrage in China
OL,6,FIn recent decades China has been
OL,7,Frocked by several food and drug
OL,8,Fscandals. One of the most shocking in
OL,9,F2008 involved the chemical
OL,10,Fcontamination of baby formula which
OL,11,Fkilled six infants and caused sickness
OL,12,Fin hundreds of thousands of others.
OL,14,FIn 2011 a "gutter oil'' scandal
OL,15,Fshocked the country and 32 people were
OL,16,Farrested for selling tonnes of cooking
OL,17,Foil which had been dredged from drains
OL,18,Fbehind restaurants, and resold.
