OL,6,FThose incidents caused a deep mistrust
OL,7,Fof domestic baby and food products -
OL,8,Fthis latest scandal has resurfaced
OL,9,Fsome of the same misgivings.
OL,11,FMany comments on the scandal have been
OL,12,Fdeleted but there are still tens of
OL,13,Fthousands of posts, with millions of
OL,14,Flikes, where people have called for
OL,15,Fthe companies and the drivers involved
OL,16,Fto be arrested and prosecuted.
OL,18,FMany have described it as "equal to
OL,19,Fpoisoning" and people complained that
OL,20,FChina "has never had food safety''.
