OL,3,CCooking oil contamination scandal
OL,4,Csparks outrage in China
OL,6,FIn one post someone pointed out that
OL,7,FChina had raised an uproar about
OL,8,FJapan's release of wastewater from the
OL,9,FFukushima nuclear plant, when it turns
OL,10,Fout the country is "feeding chemicals
OL,11,Fto its own people all along".
OL,13,FAn investigative team has been set up
OL,14,Fby the Chinese government, promising
OL,15,Fthat those responsible for any
OL,16,Fnegligence "will be severely punished
OL,17,Fin accordance with the law''.
