OL,6,FIn the case of the baby formula in
OL,7,F2008 several company executives were
OL,8,Ffound responsible, and two men were
OL,9,Fgiven death sentences.
OL,11,FThe revelations come at a politically
OL,12,Fsensitive time, with the Chinese
OL,13,Fgovernment preparing to meet for its
OL,14,FThird Plenum next week, when eagerly
OL,15,Fanticipated announcements are expected
OL,16,Fon what action will be taken to
OL,17,Faddress the country's economic
OL,18,Fdownturn.
