OL,3,CCooking oil contamination scandal
OL,4,Csparks outrage in China
OL,6,FSince he came to power President Xi
OL,7,Fhas stressed the importance of food
OL,8,Fsafety and the security of food
OL,9,Fsupplies.
OL,11,FIn a speech following the "gutter oil"
OL,12,Fscandal he said: "If the ruling party
OL,13,Fcannot manage something as fundamental
OL,14,Fas food safety, and even allow it to
OL,15,Fpersist without proper resolution over
OL,16,Fa long period, the party's ability to
OL,17,Fgovern will be challenged."
