OL,6,FAccording to Beijing News, companies
OL,7,Fhave been foregoing the expensive deep
OL,8,Fcleaning processes and using tankers
OL,9,Fconsecutively for fuel and cooking
OL,10,Foils largely to cut costs and save
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,FDespite the perception of Chinese
OL,14,Fstate media, it is their investigative
OL,15,Freporters who have uncovered several
OL,16,Fof the past food and drug safety
OL,17,Fscandals.
